Openpay,is,an,integrated,service,solution,for,Latin,America,that,allows,users,to,accept,and,send,payments,online,without,dealing,with,banking,systems,compliance,fraud,and,security,The,Openpay,API,allows,to,handle,Charges,from,cards,banks,and,stores,Payouts,to,debit,cards,and,banks,accounts,Transfers,between,accounts,Customers,Cards,Bank,Accounts,Plans,Subscriptions,and,Fees,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON